text: Lokuge Dinesh Chandimal born 18 November 1989 is a professional Sri Lankan cricketer and a former captain of the Sri Lanka national cricket team. A handy right-handed middle order batter who sometimes plays as the wicket-keeper. == References == == Other websites == * * Dinesh Chandimal's profile page on Wisden Category:1989 births Category:Sri Lankan cricketers
